These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, traveling, filmmaking, board-games, magic-tricks
City: london, boston, venice, marseilles, rome
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, disco, metal, punk, jazz
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, lily, zinnia, iris
 1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is the person traveling to london##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the fan electronic is on the left of the fan metal##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who growslily##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the fan disco and the person traveling to rome##2
12. the fan punk is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
13. the fan jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Hobby      | baking        | traveling | magic-tricks     | filmmaking   | board-games |
| City   | venice     | boston      | marseilles | rome   | london    |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco     | electronic | metal | jazz  |
| Flower           | tulip | lily      | iris     | zinnia   | marigold     |

