.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, aquamarine, yellow, blood-red, amber
5 different games are played: bridge, whist, mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, iced-tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, scientific, comedy, mystery
 1. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is between the person drinking tea and the person playing monopoly##2
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person drinking juice is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
11. the person drinking juice is the person who likes yellow##1
12. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Color         | blood-red | pink | amber    | aquamarine  | yellow    |
| Game   | monopoly    | whist       | mah-jongg      | bridge | canasta        |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate     | tea    | lemonade  | juice     |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific    | documentary | mystery | comedy | time-travel |

