The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, metal, salsa, d&b, r&b
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, brown, mauve, lilac, light-blue
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, nurse, coach, dancer, engineer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, orchid, rose, azalea, bellflower
 1. the engineer is between the person who growsorchid and the nurse##2
 2. the coach is on the left of the dancer##1
 3. the fan metal is the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the fan reggae is on the right of the engineer##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the fan metal##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the fan metal##1
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
10. the coach is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsrose is between the coach and the person who likes mauve##2
12. the fan d&b is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
13. the fan salsa is on the left of the fan d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre    | salsa       | d&b    | r&b | metal  | reggae        |
| Color       | light-blue | orange | mauve  | lilac | brown    |
| Job       | coach        | dancer   | nurse  | engineer   | architect |
| Flower   | azalea       | rose      | bellflower      | poppy | orchid  |

