.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, baccarat, aristoff, alhambra
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, coral, azure, lavender, amber
City: berlin, edinburgh, hamburg, miami, paris
There 5 different types of food: tomato, pear, zucchini, raspberry, cherry
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who likes azure##2
 3. the aristoff-smoker is the person who likes lavender##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who likes amber and the person eating pear##2
 7. the person eating raspberry is the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
10. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person who likes azure is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
13. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar      | siglo      | tiparillo         | aristoff      | baccarat | alhambra     |
| Color           | coral | azure | lavender | amber    | ivory  |
| City   | miami  | edinburgh    | berlin | hamburg    | paris |
| Food   | zucchini  | pear        | tomato   | raspberry    | cherry     |

