.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, gospel, ambient, techno, jazz
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, drama, action, comedy, animation
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, apricot, cucumber, banana, radish
House: futuristic, cape-cod, art-deco, palace, gothic-revival
 1. the person eating radish is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the fan jazz is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating apricot is between the person watching spy movies and the person eating lettuce##2
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the fan ambient is between the futuristic house and the fan jazz##2
 8. the fan gospel is between the fan techno and the fan trance##2
 9. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan trance##1
10. the fan trance is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Music-Genre         | jazz  | ambient | techno   | gospel      | trance |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | comedy    | drama | animation | action      |
| Food           | cucumber | apricot    | lettuce       | banana     | radish      |
| House     | art-deco | gothic-revival        | futuristic  | cape-cod        | palace    |

