.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, goldfish, rat, lizard
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, sunflower, zinnia, rose
There 5 different types of food: apricot, corn, avocado, strawberry, pumpkin
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, poker, go, bridge
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growsrose is between the person playing go and the person eating pumpkin##2
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the person who growsrose is the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating apricot is between the person playing bridge and the person eating avocado##2
 6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person eating corn##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating corn##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Pet         | goldfish    | lizard  | fish  | guinea-pig      | rat |
| Flower   | azalea    | rose   | zinnia | sunflower | balloon-flower   |
| Food   | avocado | apricot    | pumpkin    | strawberry       | corn         |
| Game   | go  | scrabble | bridge    | poker     | mah-jongg      |

 